members.member:

Gets or sets the layout configuration for the items in the map legend. This property allows you to define how individual legend items are arranged within the legend.


It accepts the value and its default value is null.

Note: 
Users should not add items explicitly inside the layout. 
Users must initialize the layout instance only and should not bind the item source to the layout.

